reviewText: he's witty,  self-effacing and introspective.  Rare qualities for an astronaut.  This is a short,  but fun talk from one of the few men to step foot on the moon.

Great movie however whomever wrote the description stated that Alan Bean "Apollo 13" astronaut was fourth person to walk on the moon. Now that a fail because Alan Bean was the LMP on Apollo 12...oops! LOL!
